1-2 Yam tamtoghon to ndug ndug, alooŋ saveeŋ tiou tonene.
Pasa, Maaron pale igham mulin ghou pa mateeŋ.
Eemoghon you irau nagham makau, ma mekmek to tineep ila sirsiir tiam lolo ne maau.
Tamtoghon to mata iŋgal tau pa laghooŋ toni, nene pale napatooŋ ulaaŋ tiou pani, ve nagham mulini.
