Ve inimale ye itaghon ŋgar to daba to watooŋrau to taan titaghoni, tone sawa to Maaron ighur sambam ve taan ve inim, ye ighamgham yabyabuuŋ ve mateeŋ. Eemoghon maau. Aazne, nene sawa to Maaron ipasob uraat toni. Tauto Krisi izi inim taan, ve iyokia tau ve imaat, leso ireu sosor toit ve ipasob samia tapiri. Ve uraat tonenen, ye ighami pa ee moghon ve isob. Irau ighami muul maau.
Ve ŋgar to talup ghiit pa suŋuuŋ, nene tapuli malep. You nasavia saveeŋ tonene pasa, tamtoghon tiam pida naghodi perperia pa lupuuŋ tiam maau. Tovenen matamim iŋgal ve alup gham ve awapalotin gham. Pasa, sawa to Tiina toit, nene inim igharau wa.
Tovenen aghita. Abaram, ye ŋgeu ee moghon kat, ve inim olman waat wa. Eemoghon yesuru azuwa Sara tipoop, ve tamtoghon to tivot ila toni, yes katindi kat. Irau tanin di maau. Pasa, timasa tinim naol tinimale pitum to sambam paroŋania, ve magargaar to naari.
to pale iuul ghiit tasob. Leso tasob taneep deŋiaad kat ila mata. Ve ye lolo pa yes tighami muuŋ malep. Ye ighaze ilup ghiit toman di, ve iit tasob taghami raraate.
Ve tonene moghon maau. Pale natok sambam paroŋania paam.”
Ataam tonowen pale ineep tovene itaghoni taghoni gha ila.
Eemoghon igharaat tau maau, ve imundig ila, ve rikia moghon lolo imaagh pa nagho muul.
Pughu tonene to tiwaat Abaram tighaze ye Maaron ita ite.
“Yes to tipait taudi izadi, nene Maaron ighurghur koi padi ve itatan di.
Yam toŋvetaz, ighaze tamtoghon tiam eta iyel pa ataam to saveeŋ onoon, yam lemim uraat pa apasaluŋgani, ve aghami imuul inim itaghon ataam to Maaron.
Saveeŋ tonowen, nene varu poia to tivotia payam.
Muuŋ, yam aneep animale sipsip to tisagsag. Ve aazne, amuul anim to Ŋginiiŋ tiam Krisi wa. Ye Ŋgeu to mata pa anunumim irau sawa isob.
Yes timaat pasa, tamtoghon tisob to taan to tigham sosor, Maaron ighur atia padi. Eemoghon ila uraat to Avuvu Patabuaŋ, aazne anunudi tineep matadi iyaryaar.
Ye ariaŋa, ve tapiri toman pooz toni, nene inepneep tovene irau sawa isob. Onoon.
Ndiran tonanan ledi mayadi maau. Matadi samia tinimale ŋgavuun. Ve ival tiina pale titaghon di pa ŋgar todi samia tonowen. Tovenen ŋgar to tighami, pale inim pughu pa tamtoghon tipiyaav saveeŋ velegiiŋ pa ataam to saveeŋ onoon.
Eemoghon iit taghurghur mataad pa sambam paghu ve taan paghu to pale tivot titaghon saveeŋ mbuaaŋ to Maaron. Sambam ve taan papaghu tonowen, ŋgar deŋia moghon pale ineep ila.
you nambood saveeŋ tonene ilat tiam pasa, ila Yesu Krisi iza, Tamaan Maaron ireu sosor tiam isob ilale wa.
Sawa to aghur ila muuŋ ve inim, yam aloŋlooŋ saveeŋ tovene: Iit irau lolood pa tauud ve tagham poian tauud.
Ŋgar to lolood pa tamtoghon ve tagham poian di, nene Maaron ŋgar toni. Tovenen ighaze iit takis ŋgar tonene tuŋia, ve tataghoni irau sawa isob, nene pale taneep tuŋia ila to Maaron, ve ye ineep tuŋia inim toit, ve itiŋa talup ghiit tanim ee moghon.
Iit to tataghon saveeŋ onoon, ve lolood pa Maaron ve tamtoghon paam, poia to Tamaan Maaron yesuru Natu Yesu Krisi pale iza toit, ve lolodi isamin ghiit, ve tigham ghiit taneep pooi toman lolood luuma. Onoon.
Ve agham ŋgar pa yes aŋela to muuŋ kat tizoor Maaron aliŋa. Uraat to Maaron ighuri ila nimadi ve izadi pani, toman inadi to nepooŋ to ye igham padi, yes tirere pani ve tipuli. Tauto Maaron izurun di tighau pa inadi, ve ikau di pa ravraav ariaŋadi to pale tineep irau sawa isob, ve ighur di tineep ila ndoroom tiina lolo. Leso tineep tonowe ve tisaŋan sawa tiina to Mboŋ Muri, ghoro ye iŋgabiiz di ve ighur atia padi.
Tovenen ndug tisob to taan pale tighita, ve titaŋ tiina.
“Aŋela to iŋgin lupuuŋ tiou to tineep izi ndug Pergamum, umbood saveeŋ ila pani tovene:
“Aŋela to iŋgin lupuuŋ tiou to tineep izi ndug Piladelpia, umbood saveeŋ ila pani tovene:
“Tiina toit Maaron, tapiri tiina kat. Ilib pa mbeb to naol ne.
Ghoro Sipsip to Maaron iwalab bagil ite izi, ve nalooŋ mbeb matadi yaryaara paaŋ, todi ite isaav ighaze: “Unum!”
Tovenen yes irau pitool di, ma murun di muul maau. Ve ndag irau ighaaz katin di muul maau.
Ve tandagiiŋ tiou, you naghita yes to tineep izala hos ve tilaan padi ne, ghitoŋadi tovene: Mbeb ariaŋadi to tipoon atedi pani, nene ŋgeretuŋadi kaviaaŋa inimale yab, bibiliiŋa, ve yaŋoŋa. Ve hos todi dabadi, nene inimale to laion. Ve mbeb samsamia tol tivotvot ila avodi pa tiwaghamun tamtoghon. Nene yab, mbuas, ve yaam salfa tuntunu to vuzi samia kat.
Ghoro aŋela ite to inim liim ve ru pani, ana ivib tavuur toni, ve nalooŋ ival tiina to tineep izi sambam, tisaav aliŋadi tiina tighaze: “Aa, ghara ŋgar samia to muuŋ igham pooz pa taan ne tapiri isob, ve mbeb to naol ne titaghon pooz to Maaron toit ve Mesia toni. Ve ye pale igham pooz tovene itaghoni taghoni gha ila!”
Ve tiput aghedi pa moot ve tipaiti. Pasa, ye to ighur tapiri ve iza ila to mbeb tonenen. Ve mbeb samia tonenen paam, tiput aghedi pani ve tipaiti tighaze: “Aighat, sei irau mbeb tonene? Ve sei irau iparab tomani ve ilib pani? Maau.”
Ghoro aŋela ite ivot pa Rumai Tiina to sambam we, ve imboob pa ŋgeu to ineep izala yaghur tae ighaze: “Sawa to ŋgogaaŋ aniiŋ, ighaze ivot tonene. Pasa, aniiŋ wit tiom to titub izi taan, timatu wa. Tovenen ugham buza tiom kooka tonanan, ve undeeb di tizi.”
Ghoro aŋela ite inim liim, ana igham oon toni, ve ila iliŋ mbalmbali to Maaron iŋarua mbeb samia ina to ghamuuŋ pooz. Tovenen yes to tineep ila mbeb tonowen samba, ndoroom tiina ikau di. Ve yabyabuuŋ tiina igham tamtoghon le livodi kikikia.
Ghoro aŋela tonenen isaav payou muul ighaze:
Ve yes pale tisaav pa ndug tiina Babilon tighaze: “Mbeb naol to lolom igham padi, eta igharau ghom muul maau. Mbaliiŋ tiom to popoiadi kat ve ughamgham izam padi, tisob tilaledi wa. Irau ughita di muul maau.”
Mala maau ve nalooŋ oroor tiina ivot izi sambam muul. Oroor tonowen, inimale ival tiina timboboob. Ve inimale ndug to ya katindi tiyatyaat tizi pani, ve inimale lalaav kiliŋia. Ival tiina tonowen tisaav tighaze:
Sawa tonenen, te ipul yes mateeŋa to tineep ila lolo tila. Ve Mateeŋ toman ndug to mateeŋa paam. Tipul mateeŋa tisob tila. Ghoro Maaron iŋgabiiz tamtoghon tisob itaghon ŋgar todi todi.
Ndug ndug pale tilooŋ tila ndug tonowen toman paitooŋ todi, ve tipait Maaron.
